            FixOngo – Where Fix Meets Go!
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            At FixOngo, we are committed to being your trusted partner for
            doorstep mobile repair services across Bengaluru. Our experienced
            technicians specialize in diagnosing and fixing a wide range of
            device problems quickly and reliably.
          </p>
          <img
            alt="Mobile device repair workstation with tools and circuit board on a blue mat"
            class="w-full h-auto max-h-80 h-auto object-cover rounded-lg mb-6"
            height="350"
            src="images/AboutUs/leftImg.avif"
            width="600"
          />
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We know how frustrating a broken device can be, so we’re committed
            to delivering fast and dependable repairs that have you enjoying
            your gadgets again quickly.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section class="lg:w-1/2 mt-10 lg:mt-0">
          <img
            alt="Person in gray t-shirt and black pants using smartphone, sitting on a chair"
            class="w-full h-auto mt-16 max-h-80 h-auto object-cover rounded-lg mb-6"
            height="400"
            src="images/AboutUs/rightImg.avif"
            width="600"
          />
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            We’re more than just a mobile repair service — we’re your trusted
            partners in keeping your devices running flawlessly. With over 5
            years of experience serving Bengaluru, our mission is clear: deliver
            high-quality repairs with convenient doorstep service.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our skilled technicians bring expert care to every job, ensuring
            your device is handled with precision. From cracked screens to water
            damage, battery faults to software issues, we’ve fixed it all —
            right at your doorstep.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </section>
  <!-- ----------------------------------------------------------------------- -->

  <section class="bg-[#f2f4f1]">
