          All you need to do is is to trust tech pros.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-8">
          <p class="text-[#f15a29] font-extrabold text-[40px] mb-4">01.</p>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[20px] mb-2 text-black">Contact Us</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px] font-normal leading-relaxed">
            Reach out to FixOngo via phone, WhatsApp, or our website to book a
            doorstep repair service at your convenience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8">
          <p class="text-[#f15a29] font-extrabold text-[40px] mb-4">02.</p>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[20px] mb-2 text-black">
            On-Site Visit & Quick Check
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px] font-normal leading-relaxed">
            Our technician will arrive at your location, assess the issue, and
            proceed with the necessary steps
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8">
          <p class="text-[#f15a29] font-extrabold text-[40px] mb-4">03.</p>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[20px] mb-2 text-black">
            Expert Repair
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-[16px] font-normal leading-relaxed">
            We complete most repairs right at your doorstep. If needed, we’ll
            pick up, fix, and return your device the same day.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
